An Act relative to Constitutional rights.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 Chapter 140 shall be amended by inserting the following section:-
2 Section 120A. No county, municipality, township or other community entity within the
3 Commonwealth of Massachusetts may enact, pass or enforce any law, ordinance or regulation
4 concerning the lawful ownership, use, possession, transfer, purchase, receipt or transportation of
5 weapons, antique weapons, ammunition or ammunition components.
